{"tid":411850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發][轉載有片] 屯門百佳賤男虐狗","createTime":"2017-09-24T07:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T11:16:27.000Z","uid":49388,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dac46821a7d27d5cea9969380bcb422c8f638be4","tid":411850,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775?view=permalink&amp;id=1184102885265409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D1184102885265409&d=PC25NiIE3%2FE4kWtgoT2smG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d2385e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775?view=permalink&amp;id=1184102885265409</a><br />\n<br />\n「屯門百佳賤男虐狗」<br />\n<br />\n請大家分享出去 地點係屯門寶田商場<br />\n<br />\n事緣有人放低左隻狗比百佳嘅職員睇住，唔俾佢周圍走！<br />\n<br />\n突然呢個痴線佬就大大聲嘈百佳嘅職員：<br />\n呢到點可以有隻狗架，掉隻狗出去啦！<br />\n<br />\n個職員就話：<br />\n我只可以喺度睇住隻狗唔比佢周圍走，等佢主人返嚟！<br />\n<br />\n然後個男人就發晒癲話：<br />\n屌！等我來！((即刻放低手上嘅嘢沖咗入百佳))<br />\n<br />\n片段見到佢掉狗踢狗，冇人性<br />\n<br />\n根本係虐狗，個男人時候匆匆離去，狗狗嘅主人又不在，<br />\n無奈地我不能捉住佢然後報警！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家認住呢個變態佬(生人勿近)<br />\n<br />\n（以上文字為轉載）"},{"pid":"28ecd406e349b4141ceea92333857e106e198bc5","tid":411850,"uid":52942,"like":13,"dislike":35,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:23:25.000Z","msg":"的確唔應該比狗入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仗義每多屠狗輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7975e21320bfcb11e288b715b62048af49fc388f","tid":411850,"uid":4780,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的確唔應該比狗入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仗義每多屠狗輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老母都唔應該生你條賤蓄出黎，番入佢個閪啦"},{"pid":"c35d70360e1316043ea898021300f944496e7111","tid":411850,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,