1850,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"百佳同意幫人睇住關你撚事咩 投訴百佳囉 又拉左膠黎講"},{"pid":"d373e2d435f700df6fb0bacb2e20ba03c1d77fe1","tid":411850,"uid":51505,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:24:07.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係痴撚線，竟然有人撐個阿叔<br />\n百佳唔應該有動物=虐畜合理化？<br />\n照同樣道理，你行入左私人地方，然後俾人打都係合理，照同樣道理，呢個世界唔需要有法律，人人都可以做地獄判官，呢個世代既人係咪連基本道德公義都已經唔存在，香港真係被大陸同化"},{"pid":"8bcee335f46759a54c21f7b8cde275ae0d4c7f43","tid":411850,"uid":52942,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔真係痴撚線，竟然有人撐個阿叔<br />\n百佳唔應該有動物=虐畜合理化？<br />\n照同樣道理，你行入左私人地方，然後俾人打都係合理，照同樣道理，呢個世界唔需要有法律，人人都可以做地獄判官，呢個世代既人係咪連基本道德公義都已經唔存在，香港真係被大陸同化</blockquote><br />\n將人同狗相提並論真係好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你個比喻應該係如果有人帶埋d倉鼠兔仔入去百佳，我一樣支持趕佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家d狗奴見到就眼冤，當d畜牲人咁，推車比狗坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係反智，不過你唔影響人我wfc,  今次明顯係狗主錯，百佳有食物有小朋友，你放隻狗又冇狗帶入黎，大人有責任趕走佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01982b909551cac35c0d3c2239cf1a34eddd635","tid":411850,"uid":137731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:38:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"741f8a2d45f1eb16cdd899d9dd1ba04ac2a89d3b","tid":411850,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係好撚痴線 趕就要打要踢？ 同支那豬冇分別</blockquote><br />\n癡撚線，徒手捉比狗咬個個又唔係你，你係個mon前面梗係講得口響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如攞碌撚引佢行出去呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf769c028a28545257354b224f6365181500300","tid":411850,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係芝娃娃嘅就撐個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係<br />\n撐阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a6f4edb4e5c8c52b3754269ccecc82ecaae0b9","tid":411850,"uid":21664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意就可以暴力解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位好野"},{"pid":"e49dab03f7387c8c485e60298d051811a9b3af14","tid":411850,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔鍾意就可以暴力解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位好野</blockquote><br />\n都估到呢度會有啲咩迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有人話連登有愛 愛個阿叔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2227b501280c0339d65bc613f332f01dee4bea","tid":411850,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係芝娃娃嘅就撐個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係, 癲狗 vs 癲佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170ac3dc930fdf369bd9616f164fed44f7602030","tid":411850,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔鍾意就可以暴力解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位好野</blockquote><br />\n和與和平感化狗主與狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}